# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Profile Builder — Environment Configuration
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to .env and fill in YOUR values.
# This is the SINGLE config file that drives all MCP tools.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
# ║  1. LinkedIn Archive                                                ║
# ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝
# Export your data from: https://www.linkedin.com/mypreferences/d/download-my-data
# Extract the ZIP, paste the folder path below.
#
# Example: C:\Users\you\Downloads\LinkedInExport
# Example: /home/you/Downloads/LinkedInExport

LINKEDIN_ARCHIVE_PATH=

# ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
# ║  2. GitHub Profile                                                  ║
# ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝
# Your GitHub profile URL or username.
#
# Example: https://github.com/your-username
# Example: your-username

GITHUB_PROFILE=

# (Optional) GitHub Personal Access Token for private repos.
# Create one at: https://github.com/settings/tokens?type=beta
# Permissions needed: Contents (read), Metadata (read)
# Without a token, only public repos are accessible.

GITHUB_TOKEN=

# ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
# ║  3. Coding Profiles                                                 ║
# ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝
# Paste your coding profile URLs separated by commas.
# Supported: LeetCode, Codeforces (more can be added)
#
# Example: https://leetcode.com/u/your-username, https://codeforces.com/profile/your-username

CODING_PROFILES=

# ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
# ║  4. Resume History Folder                                         ║
# ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝
# Folder containing your past resume files (PDF and/or DOCX).
# Files are sorted by last-modified date to reconstruct your career timeline.
#
# Example: C:\Users\you\Documents\Resumes
# Example: /home/you/resumes

RESUME_HISTORY_PATH=
